<page-meta page-style="background:#071319" />

<view class="page safe-bottom">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="orbit orbit-one"></view><view class="orbit orbit-two"></view>
    <view class="planet"><view class="planet-glow"></view><view class="continent continent-one"></view><view class="continent continent-two"></view></view>
    <view class="eyebrow">EARTH · 4.54 BILLION YEARS</view>
    <view class="hero-title">地球编年史</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">从一颗炽热的新生行星，滑向正在学习与创造的人工智能时代。</view>
    <view class="hero-stats">
      <view class="stat"><text class="stat-value">45.4亿</text><text class="stat-label">年时间跨度</text></view><view class="stat-divider"></view>
      <view class="stat"><text class="stat-value">{{eventCount}}</text><text class="stat-label">个关键节点</text></view><view class="stat-divider"></view>
      <view class="stat"><text class="stat-value">29</text><text class="stat-label">个时期与章节</text></view>
    </view>
    <view class="scroll-cue"><view class="scroll-line"></view><text>向下滑动，时间开始流动</text></view>
  </view>

  <view class="filter-panel">
    <view class="filter-heading"><view><text>时代与时期</text><text>当前 {{filteredCount}} / {{eventCount}} 个事件</text></view><view class="mode-switch"><button class="{{mode === 'chapter' ? 'active' : ''}}" bindtap="selectMode" data-mode="chapter">章节模式</button><button class="{{mode === 'deep' ? 'active' : ''}}" bindtap="selectMode" data-mode="deep">深时间比例</button></view></view>
    <scroll-view class="era-nav" scroll-x="true" enhanced="true" show-scrollbar="false"><view class="era-nav-inner"><button class="era-chip {{selectedEraId === item.id ? 'selected' : ''}}" wx:for="{{eras}}" wx:key="id" bindtap="selectEra" data-id="{{item.id}}"><view class="era-dot" style="background:{{item.color}}"></view><text>{{item.name}}</text></button></view></scroll-view>
    <scroll-view class="period-nav" scroll-x="true" enhanced="true" show-scrollbar="false"><view class="period-nav-inner"><button class="period-chip {{selectedPeriodId === item.id ? 'selected' : ''}}" wx:for="{{periodOptions}}" wx:key="id" bindtap="selectPeriod" data-id="{{item.id}}" style="border-color:{{selectedPeriodId === item.id ? item.color : 'rgba(230,245,239,.1)'}}">{{item.name}}</button></view></scroll-view>
  </view>

  <view class="timeline-intro">
    <text class="section-kicker">THE LONG VIEW</text><text class="section-title">一条不断加速的时间河流</text>
    <text wx:if="{{mode === 'chapter'}}" class="section-copy">章节模式按阅读顺序排列，卡片距离不代表真实时间比例。</text>
    <text wx:else class="section-copy">深时间模式只依据各时期起点采用对数压缩间距，用于感受数量级差异；它不是事件精确日期图，也不表达持续时间。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="timeline mode-{{mode}}">
    <view class="timeline-spine"></view>
    <block wx:for="{{events}}" wx:key="id">
      <view wx:if="{{item.isChapterStart}}" class="era-marker" style="margin-top:{{mode === 'deep' ? item.deepGap : 58}}rpx"><view class="era-marker-line"></view><view class="era-marker-pill" style="border-color:{{item.periodColor}};color:{{item.periodColor}}">{{item.periodName}}</view><text class="era-marker-range">{{item.topEraName}}</text></view>
      <view id="event-{{item.id}}" class="event-row">
        <view class="event-node" style="border-color:{{item.periodColor}};box-shadow:0 0 0 8rpx {{item.glow}}"><view class="event-node-core" style="background:{{item.periodColor}}"></view></view>
        <view class="event-card" hover-class="event-card-active" bindtap="openEvent" data-id="{{item.id}}">
          <view class="event-media"><media-image media-id="{{item.mediaId}}" variant="thumbnail" ratio="16:9" alt="{{item.title}}科学图片" placeholder-theme="rock" /></view>
          <view class="period-color-bar" style="background:{{item.periodColor}}"></view>
          <view class="event-card-body">
            <view class="card-topline"><view class="category" style="color:{{item.periodColor}}">{{item.category}}</view><view class="card-arrow">↗</view></view>
            <view class="event-time">{{item.displayTime}}</view><view class="event-title">{{item.title}}</view><view class="event-summary">{{item.summary}}</view>
            <view class="card-footer"><text>查看说明、图片与来源</text><view class="footer-line" style="background:{{item.periodColor}}"></view></view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </block>
    <view wx:if="{{!events.length}}" class="timeline-empty">当前筛选下没有事件，请切换时代或时期。</view>
    <view class="now-node"><view class="now-pulse"></view><view class="now-core"></view><text>你在这里 · 2026</text></view>
  </view>

  <view class="closing"><text class="closing-kicker">TO BE CONTINUED</text><text class="closing-title">历史没有终点</text><text class="closing-copy">每一代人都站在漫长过去的最前沿。下一张卡片，会由我们共同写下。</text><view class="closing-actions"><button bindtap="openPeriods">浏览29个时期</button><button bindtap="openQuiz">测测你的远古身份</button></view></view>
</view>
